Class HajimariApplicationWrapper

java.lang.Object
us.ullberg.startpunkt.objects.kubernetes.BaseKubernetesObject
us.ullberg.startpunkt.objects.kubernetes.HajimariApplicationWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
KubernetesObject
public class HajimariApplicationWrapper extends BaseKubernetesObject
Wrapper for Hajimari application custom resources. Provides access to application properties from the Kubernetes resource spec.
